---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import SEO from '../components/SEO.astro';

const canonicalPath = '/proof';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Proof & Templates | NaughtyCamSpot"
  description="Sample Growth Ops deliverables for weekly reporting, posting packs, and campaign calendars."
>
  <SEO
    slot="head"
    title="Proof & Templates | NaughtyCamSpot"
    description="Sample Growth Ops deliverables for weekly reporting, posting packs, and campaign calendars."
    path={canonicalPath}
  />

  <section class="space-y-8">
    <div class="content-card space-y-4">
      <p class="hero-tagline">Proof</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl text-white sm:text-5xl">Sample Weekly Ops Report</h1>
      <p class="max-w-3xl text-sm text-white/75">
        This page shows practical samples from our AI-Fulfilled Model Growth Ops workflow: a weekly report layout, posting pack examples,
        and a 7-day campaign push calendar structure. If you used our older naming, this includes a Sample Promo Packet and Sample Weekly Report format.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="content-card space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Posting Pack Example</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/30 p-4 text-sm text-white/75">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-white">Caption examples (A/B test style)</p>
            <ul class="mt-1 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
              <li>"Live in 15 — tonight is all about fast goals + surprise unlocks."</li>
              <li>"Late-night room opens at 11:30. Tip menu refreshed. See you there."</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-white">Title examples</p>
            <ul class="mt-1 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
              <li>"Going live now — new goal ladder + cozy vibe tonight"</li>
              <li>"First stream of the week: token milestones + requests open"</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-white">Daily posting cadence example</p>
            <ul class="mt-1 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
              <li>Mon/Wed/Fri: pre-live post at T-45 and T-10</li>
              <li>Tue/Thu: retention post + poll</li>
              <li>Sun: recap + what to shoot next prompt</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="content-card space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Sample Weekly Ops Report</h2>
        <div class="space-y-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/30 p-4 text-sm text-white/75">
          <p class="font-semibold text-white">Weekly KPI snapshot (layout example)</p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
            <li>Link clicks: 1,284 (+18% vs prior week)</li>
            <li>Follower delta: +92 net</li>
            <li>Best hooks: "live in 10" + "goal ladder unlocked"</li>
            <li>Next actions: tighten T-10 reminder, test shorter titles, repeat top opener twice this week</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="content-card space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Campaign Example (7-day goal push calendar)</h2>
        <div class="space-y-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/30 p-4 text-sm text-white/75">
          <p class="font-semibold text-white">Goal push calendar blocks</p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
            <li>Day 1–2: baseline schedule and hooks</li>
            <li>Day 3–4: run top caption variants, tighten reminders</li>
            <li>Day 5–6: push high-intent offers and countdown sequences</li>
            <li>Day 7: recap, retention post, next-week campaign brief</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="content-card space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Operator notes example</h2>
        <div class="space-y-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/30 p-4 text-sm text-white/75">
          <p class="font-semibold text-white">Show script blocks</p>
          <p>"Big tip window in the next 10 minutes — drop your request and let's push the next milestone together."</p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-white">Tip-trigger notes</p>
          <p>"If momentum drops, trigger the short countdown block and return to the top-converting opener."</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Trust posture + non-negotiables</h2>
      <ul class="grid gap-3 text-sm text-white/75 md:grid-cols-2">
        <li class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3">No passwords/logins required</li>
        <li class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3">No exclusivity requirements</li>
        <li class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3">Model owns accounts and content</li>
        <li class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3">No spam / no mass unsolicited DMs</li>
        <li class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3">Cancel anytime</li>
        <li class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3">No earnings guarantees</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-xs text-white/60">
        Results vary by niche, consistency, and platform conditions. These examples are educational templates and do not promise earnings
        outcomes.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <p class="text-sm text-white/75">Want this implemented as a weekly system? Review packages or start your promo application.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-rose-gold/70 bg-rose-gold px-6 py-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-midnight shadow-glow transition hover:-translate-y-1"
          href="/packages"
        >
          View packages
        </a>
        <a
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-transparent px-6 py-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white transition hover:border-white/40 hover:bg-white/5"
          href="/apply/promo"
        >
          Apply for promotion
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
